&CHANGE-SLAVE-WEATHER Storm Maker=$slave *: &weathertype #114=%0
&INSIDE Storm Maker=$inside *: @dolist setunion(iter(children(#512), children(##)), iter(children(#510), children(##))) = @pemit/contents ## = [capstr(%0)]
&ZONE Storm Maker=$zone *=*: @dolist inzone(%0) = @pemit/contents ## = [capstr(%1)]
&SEARCH-ATTRIBUTE Storm Maker=$search *=*: @dolist search(eroom=\[hasattr(##, %0)\]) = @pemit/contents ## = [capstr(%1)]
@Desc Storm Maker=This item can be used to trigger local storm effects. It should be set wizard and safe, and should be kept in the Auxiliary room when not in use.
